text: Zyzz (Aziz Shavershian) is a Russian bodybuilder. He was born in 24 of March 1989 died in 2011 while on holiday in Thailand. He is known for "The Zyzz Pose" which is a famous pose in bodybuilding. Category:Russian sportspeople Category:Bodybuilders Category:1989 births Category:2011 deaths
title: Aziz Shavershian
